The paper discusses a novel approach to vector similarity searching over dense semantic representations of words and documents, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper proposes a scalable vector database, which involves database systems (cs.DB).
